text: Osmo Juhani Ala-Honkola (12 May 1939 - 14 November 2020) was a Finnish sports shooter. He competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics and the 1972 Summer Olympics. He was born in Kuortane, Finland. Ala-Honkola died on 14 November 2020 in Vaasa at the age of 81. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Olympians for Finland Category:Sport shooters
